1) To participate in a chess tournament, you need to be a member on the Chess.com club
2) You must not be banned from chess events on the server
3) You must not be banned from the Chess.com club
4) You must not be banned from the server
5) You need to sign up for the tournament at https://sparty18.me/forms
6) You need to be online 2 hours before the tournament starts
7) You need to have your DMs open to allow for check ins to occur
8) You need to be on the chess VC within 5 minutes of the tournament starting
9) You need to be on the chess VC for the duration of the tournament
10) You need to be able to hear the tournament host

If you are unable to meet any of these requirements, DM the chess manager to discuss your situation. They will be able to help you out.